      <title>三星发誓要在AI记忆市场中收回地面</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/samsung-vows-to-reclaim-ground-in-ai-memory-market-with-rollout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司保证今年加强其在高带宽记忆芯片市场中的地位，以回应股东对其在有利可图的人工智能领域表现不佳的批评。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/samsung-vows-to-reclaim-ground-in-ai-memory-market-with-rollout</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 10:12:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普喜欢AI，但他的关税增加了数据中心的成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-s-ai-embrace-threatened-by-tariff-costs-to-businesses</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统都参加了人工智能，并为其提供权力的数据中心；但是他的关税可能会为美国企业花费数千亿美元建造新费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/trump-s-ai-embrace-threatened-by-tariff-costs-to-businesses</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的应用程序关闭是给墨西哥卡特尔的礼物</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-19/trump-cbp-one-app-shutdown-is-a-gift-to-mexico-cartel-smugglers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ CBP One，该应用程序帮助安排了庇护会议，在移民辩论的两面都对批评家进行了批评。但这为非法走私提供了可靠的替代方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2025-03-19/trump-cbp-one-app-shutdown-is-a-gift-to-mexico-cartel-smugglers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 09:00:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>自2023年以来销售后，腾讯加快AI的支出增长最快</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tencent-grows-fastest-in-a-year-after-spate-of-holiday-game-hits</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Tencent Holdings Ltd.概述了计划在自2023年以来的最快收入增长速度后，计划大幅提高AI基础设施支出的计划，这表明中国最有价值的公司打算打算在后Deepseek时代与竞争对手保持同步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tencent-grows-fastest-in-a-year-after-spate-of-holiday-game-hits</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 08:37:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cathie Wood在近一年内首次出售Meta股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/cathie-wood-sells-meta-shares-for-first-time-in-nearly-a-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Cathie Wood的ARK Investment Management LLC正在大约一年来首次削减其在Meta Platforms Inc.的股份，这是美国大型科技股票的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/cathie-wood-sells-meta-shares-for-first-time-in-nearly-a-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 06:20:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Morgan Stanley关闭了有争议的SK Hynix股票的销售电话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/morgan-stanley-closes-controversial-sell-call-on-sk-hynix-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利（Morgan Stanley）分析师将SK Hynix Inc.升级为同等重量级的体重不足，称他们去年9月降级了他们的降级，因为该股票自那以后对该公司在提供最先进的存储芯片方面的前景感到乐观。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/morgan-stanley-closes-controversial-sell-call-on-sk-hynix-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:55:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小米计划扩大北京电动汽车工厂以满足需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/xiaomi-plans-to-expand-beijing-ev-factory-to-meet-surging-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士说，小米公司正在扩大北京一家计划中的第二辆电动汽车工厂的规模，此前其第一款型号的成功促使亿万富翁联合创始人雷·尼·朱尼（Lei Jun）将今年的销售目标提高到350,000辆汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/xiaomi-plans-to-expand-beijing-ev-factory-to-meet-surging-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:36:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Anta Sports股份跌至全年的运营利润率。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/anta-sports-2024-sales-exceed-estimate-after-signing-nba-star</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在该公司报告2024年的运营利润率低于预期的营业利润率之后，香港的Anta Sports Ltd.股价下跌了7.4％。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/anta-sports-2024-sales-exceed-estimate-after-signing-nba-star</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 04:14:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税威胁刺激TSMC的台湾同行寻求我们扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tariff-threats-spur-tsmc-s-taiwan-peers-to-seek-us-expansion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[3月，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统和台湾半导体制造公司的C. C. C. Wei走进了罗斯福室，揭开了美国历史上最大的外国投资之一：1000亿美元的赌注，可以在美国再次进行高端筹码。对于特朗普来说，这是在上任第43天品尝的时刻。对于理查德·李（Richard Lee），看着将近8,000英里的地方，这是一个呼吁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-19/tariff-threats-spur-tsmc-s-taiwan-peers-to-seek-us-expansion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Mar 2025 03:47:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>WISETECH发现创始人白色误导的董事会，不采取任何行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/wisetech-s-white-failed-to-fully-disclose-relationships-to-board</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Wisetech Global Ltd.不会针对创始人理查德·怀特（Richard White）采取任何行动，即使调查发现他未能与雇员和供应商完全披露个人关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-18/wisetech-s-white-failed-to-fully-disclose-relationships-to-board</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Mar 2025 23:25:36 GMT</pubDate>
